name: Shirley Weber, PhD
tweet: "For the sake of the nation, we must end the legislative filibuster in the Senate across the board. An unwritten Senate practice, born out of a mistake by Aaron Burr, has metastasized to obstruct progress on countless important issues."

name: Shirley Weber, PhD
tweet: "Over the years, multiple voting rights bills have died in the United States Senate, thanks to the arcane practice of the filibuster. In 2021 alone, three good bills have been stopped; the For the People Act, the John Lewis Voting Rights Act and the Freedom to Vote Act."
